  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n1. Create a new community and send out invites to a bunch of users.\r\n2. Observe the number of community members slowly increasing as people accept your invite.\r\n3. Restart the client and observe the number of members rapidly increasing once the client has loaded the community again.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nI expect all community joiners to be tracked in real time, without having to restart the client.\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: Status Desktop 0.8\r\n- Operating System: macOS\r\n\r\n",
